Nucleic Acid Testing for COVID-19 Situation
As the table 2 indicates, the positive rate was less than 10% from February to May 2021. However, the new test number of people is around 0.4-0.5 thousand people per day, which is almost half of the other months in 2021. In late August, there are more people have been tested than ever in 2021.



